Package org.gitective.core

Class Summary
Assert Assert utilities that all throw IllegalArgumentException that will have a non-null/non-empty message.
BlobUtils Utilities for dealing with Git blobs.
Check Utility methods for various generic checks such as equality.
CommitFinder Commit finder class for locating commits based on combining TreeFilter and RevFilter instances and performing a RevWalk on one or more Git repositories.
CommitUtils Utilities for dealing with Git commits.
PathFilterUtils Utilities for filtering paths in a repository
PersonComparator PersonIdent comparator that compares the name and email address.
RepositoryService Base service class for working with one or more Repository instances.
RepositoryUtils Utilities for dealing with Git repositories.
RepositoryUtils.RefDiff Wrapper class for a remote and local ref that are different
TreeUtils Utilities for dealing with Git trees.
 

Exception Summary
GitException Git exception class.
